==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-atheist.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Hyphenation===
:a&middot;the&middot;ist

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A person who does not have a [[belief]] that one or more [[deity|deities]] or [[god]]s exist. (weak atheism)
# A person who believes that no god exists (strong atheism)
# A person who feels convinced that all references to [[gods]] are rooted in [[fiction]] and/or ancient [[:w:superstition|superstition]].

